Ingenious Irrigation
Founder: Austin Wilson
Overview: Ingenious Irrigation is an AI-powered smart irrigation system that uses computer vision
and sensors to optimize watering and detect leaks in real time.
Problem: Traditional sprinkler systems waste water due to fixed schedules and undetected failures.
Solution: Camera-based lawn health detection, zone-level AI control, automatic shutoff on leaks.
Market: Homeowners, HOAs, environmental partners, smart home ecosystem.
Business Model: Installation + recurring monthly AI subscription.
Impact: Reduced water waste, healthier landscapes, lower costs.